a-flight-allege-antisemitism-report-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELufthansa%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20fined%20%244%20million%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20after%20it%20was%20found%20to%20have%20discriminated%20against%20128%20Jewish%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20DoT%2C%20the%20German%20flag%20carrier's%20fine%20is%20the%20largest%20issued%20against%20an%20airline%20for%20civil-rights%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20fine%20relates%20to%20a%20May%202022%20incident%20involving%20a%20journey%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Budapest%2C%20where%20there%20was%20an%20annual%20memorial%20event%20to%20honor%20an%20Orthodox%20rabbi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20people%20were%20said%20to%20have%20misbehaved%20on%20the%20first%20flight%20to%20Frankfurt%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F100-jewish-passengers-to-get-21k-each-germanys-lufthansa-report-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELufthansa%20prevented%20128%20Jewish%20passengers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20whom%20wore%20garments%20typically%20worn%20by%20Orthodox%20Jewish%20men%20%E2%80%94%20from%20boarding%20their%20connecting%20flight%20to%20Budapest%2C%20the%20DoT%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20consent%20order%2C%20Lufthansa%20said%20as%20many%20as%2060%20passengers%20disregarded%20instructions%20to%20wear%20face%20masks%2C%20as%20was%20mandated%20under%20German%20law%20at%20the%20time%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Transportation%20Department%20found%20that%20Lufthansa%20failed%20to%20show%20its%20crew%20%26quot%3Btook%20any%20action%20to%20document%20the%20identities%20of%20specific%20passengers%20who%20engaged%20in%20misconduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYitzy%20Schmidt%2C%20a%20passenger%20on%20the%20flight%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20guilty%20by%20association%2C%20and%20that%20association%20is%20being%20an%20Orthodox%20Jew.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELufthansa%20said%20that%20it%20regrets%20denying%20boarding%20to%20the%20passengers%2C%20but%20said%20it%20was%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Binaccurate%20communications%2C%20misinterpretations%2C%20and%20misjudgments%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20discrimination%2C%20according%20to%20the%20DoT's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20agreed%20to%20pay%20the%20%244%20million%20fine%2C%20half%20of%20which%20consists%20of%20compensation%20it%20has%20already%20paid%20to%20the%20affected%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20BI%2C%20Lufthansa%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bfully%20cooperated%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20DoT's%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20also%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20respected%20corporate%20citizen%2C%20playing%20a%20meaningful%20role%20in%20shaping%20a%20more%20inclusive%20society%26quot%3B%20and%20pointed%20to%20its%20partnership%20with%20the%20American%20Jewish%20Committee%20and%20being%20the%20first%20airline%20to%20adopt%20the%20International%20Holocaust%20Remembrance%20Alliance's%20working%20definition%20of%20antisemitism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLufthansa%20will%20continue%20to%20foster%20a%20thoughtful%20dialogue%20with%20Jewish%20communities%20and%20organizations%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransportation%20Secretary%20Pete%20Buttigieg%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20should%20face%20discrimination%20when%20they%20travel%2C%20and%20today's%20action%20sends%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20airline%20industry%20that%20we%20are%20prepared%20to%20investigate%20and%20take%20action%20whenever%20passengers'%20civil%20rights%20are%20violated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flufthansa-given-record-fine-for-discriminating-128-jewish-passengers-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729081982000