%20leverage%20to%20ask%20for%20advanced%20Russian%20systems%20or%20the%20designs%20to%20build%20them%2C%20from%20submarines%20and%20fighter%20jets%20to%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missiles%20for%20its%20growing%20nuclear%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-worrying-military-tech-north-korea-could-get-from-russia-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epledged%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20North%20Korea%20with%20satellite%20launches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20without%20Russian%20systems%20or%20technology%20transfers%2C%20North%20Korea%20stands%20to%20gain%20in%20another%20notable%20way%3A%20by%20getting%20combat-adjacent%20experience%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20North%20Koreans%20who%20rarely%20engage%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20undoubtedly%20three%20classes%20of%20North%20Korean%20personnel%20in%20Russia%20at%20the%20present%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Bermudez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20there%20are%20embassy%20workers%2C%20%26quot%3Btypically%20counselors%20and%20military%20attaches%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20are%20there%20to%20soak%20up%20information%20about%20the%20rapidly%20changing%20nature%20of%20conflict%20on%20the%20Ukrainian%20battlefield%2C%20including%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Western%20military%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20have%20Western%20air%20defense%20systems%20been%20successful%3F%20If%20so%2C%20which%20ones%3F%20Anything%20they%20can%20find%20out%20about%20the%20equipment%2C%20its%20vulnerabilities%2C%20operational%20procedures%2C%26quot%3B%20Bermudez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20is%20also%20sending%20representatives%20from%20the%20manufacturers%20of%20military%20equipment%20it's%20providing%2C%20who%20act%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20babysitter%20to%20ensure%20it%20arrives%20in%20a%20usable%20condition%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinally%2C%20there%20are%20munitions%20experts%2C%26quot%3B%20Bermudez%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20engineers%20and%20technicians%20who%20know%20how%20to%20operate%20the%20weapons%20and%20are%20also%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20ones%20who%20visit%20the%20battlefield%20to%20see%20them%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Iranian%20experts%20have%20assisted%20Russians%20with%20Shahed%20attack%20drones%2C%20Ukrainian%20officials%20have%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20job%20is%20to%20train%20their%20counterparts%2C%20troubleshoot%20problems%2C%20and%20document%20successes%20and%20failures%20of%20military%20products%20in%20a%20real%20war%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20they%20learn%20there%20may%20be%20extremely%20valuable%20back%20home%20%E2%80%94%20they%20send%20detailed%20reports%20that%20are%20absorbed%20by%20North%20Korean%20military%20training%20authorities%2C%20potentially%20feeding%20into%20military%20manuals%20and%20training%20plans%2C%20and%20providing%20fodder%20for%20design%20or%20doctrinal%20changes%2C%20Bermudez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20also%20sends%20technical%20know-how%20and%20better%20parts%20as%20they%20tinker%20with%20the%20North%20Korean%20munitions%2C%20Bermudez%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Russians%20can%20say%2C%20'Oh%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20your%20guidance%20system.%20You%20might%20want%20to%20do%20A%2C%20B%2C%20and%20C%20or%20incorporate%20this%20gyroscope%20instead%20of%20the%20gyroscope%20you're%20using%20%E2%80%94%20or%20we%20can%20supply%20you%20with%20better%20gyroscopes.'%20That%20sort%20of%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20you%20can%20see%20your%20weapons%20fired%20in%20a%20real%20war%20situation%20%26quot%3Bthe%20better%20your%20system%20can%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20North%20Koreans%20are%20having%20an%20incredible%2C%20unique%20opportunity%20to%20do%20that.%20And%20they're%20getting%20paid%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bermudez%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3c70105-9926-4593-8b6d-007b1d6854e8%5C%22%3EPropping%20up%20an%20ailing%20regime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2Fresearch%2F2024%2F04%2Fthe-hollowing-out-of-kim-jong-uns-north-korea%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAn%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace%2C%20published%20in%20April%2C%20argued%20that%20the%20expensive%20pursuit%20of%20hyper-militarization%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20widespread%20extreme%20poverty%20that%20is%20now%20endangering%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2025-30%25%20of%20the%20territory's%20GDP%20has%20been%20committed%20to%20the%20military%2C%20it%20said%2C%20which%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Fnorth-korea-nuclear-weapons-missile-tests-military-capabilities%23chapter-title-0-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20included%20the%20fourth-largest%20army%20in%20the%20world%20as%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20the%20lucrative%20supply%20partnership%20with%20Russia%20a%20lifeline%20for%20Kim's%20regime%2C%20Bennett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20North%20Korean%20elite%2C%20there's%20also%20a%20hunger%20for%20consumer%20goods%2C%20which%20Russia's%20support%20can%20help%20to%20provide%2C%20Bennett%20said.%20But%20he%20argued%20that%20sending%20North%20Koreans%20abroad%20as%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20comes%20at%20some%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20October%2C%20six%20North%20Korean%20officials%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20strike%20in%20occupied%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyivpost.com%2Fpost%2F40037%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Kyiv%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20report%20Business%20Insider%20could%20not%20independently%20verify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20one%20that's%20%26quot%3Bgot%20to%20reverberate%20back%20in%20North%20Korea%2C%26quot%3B%20Benne