20in%20drawing%20and%20crafting%20with%20young%20women%20at%20the%20Girls%20Inc.%20in%20the%20Greater%20Santa%20Barbara%20area.%20While%20Meghan%20Markle%20was%20dressed%20elegantly%2C%20people%20noticed%20that%20her%20engagement%20ring%20was%20missing.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20iconic%20ring%2C%20designed%20by%20Prince%20Harry%20in%202017%2C%20holds%20deep%20personal%20significance.%20It%20features%20two%20diamonds%20from%20Princess%20Diana's%20collection%20and%20one%20from%20Botswana%20%E2%80%93%20symbolising%20the%20couple's%20connection%20to%20Harry's%20late%20mother%20and%20the%20country%20they%20visited%20early%20in%20their%20relationship.%20The%20engagement%20ring%2C%20set%20on%20a%20simple%20gold%20band%2C%20has%20been%20a%20hallmark%20of%20Meghan's%20style%20since%20Harry%20proposed%20at%20Kensington%20Palace.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThough%20without%20her%20engagement%20ring%2C%20Markle%20was%20wearing%20her%20wedding%20band.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIf%20this%20wasn't%20filmed%20last%20week%20I%20would%20wonder%20if%20Meghan%20is%20copying%20Catherine%20again%20by%20not%20wearing%20here%20engagement%20ring%20and%20just%20her%20wedding%20and%20eternity%20band.%20She%20did%20drop%20it%20all%20last%20year%20though%2C%20so%20who%20knows.%20More%20trouble%20with%20salt%20%26amp%3B%20pepper%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxCcghtMQvi%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FxCcghtMQvi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Royal%20News%20Network%20(%40RNN_RoyalNews)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRNN_RoyalNews%2Fstatus%2F1844850541798797332%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn't%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Duchess%20was%20without%20it.%20During%20the%202023%20Invictus%20Games%20in%20Dusseldorf%2C%20Meghan%20was%20spotted%20without%20her%20engagement%20ring.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20a%20source%20told%20Page%20Six%20that%20the%20ring%20was%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20repaired.%E2%80%9D%20It%20reappeared%20on%20her%20finger%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20both%20Meghan%20Markle%20and%20Harry%20have%20embarked%20on%20several%20high-profile%20solo%20engagements.%20Prince%20Harry%20is%20travelling%20from%20New%20York%20to%20London%20and%20even%20Southern%20Africa%20promoting%20his%20philanthropic%20initiatives.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMeghan%20Markle%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20been%20focusing%20on%20her%20projects%2C%20including%20attending%20a%20glamorous%20charity%20gala%20for%20the%20Children's%20Hospital%20LA%2C%20where%20she%20was%20seen%20wearing%20her%20engagement%20ring.%20She%20has%20reportedly%20been%20putting%20more%20energy%20into%20her%20entrepreneurial%20ventures%2C%20including%20her%20growing%20lifestyle%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20separate%20public%20appearances%20have%20led%20to%20whispers%20of%20a%20growing%20distance%20between%20the%20pair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20insiders%2C%20this%20may%20be%20part%20of%20an%20evolving%20approach%20to%20how%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20navigate%20their%20professional%20and%20personal%20lives.%20A%20source%20close%20to%20the%20couple%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FWhile%2520Meghan%2520was%2520dressed%2520elegantly%2C%2520her%2520ring%2520was%2520conspicuous%2520by%2520its%2520absence.%5C%22%3EPeople%20magazine%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20clear%20that%20a%20twin-track%20approach%20is%20evolving.%20The%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20have%20now%20hit%20their%20stride%20as%20individuals%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20as%20a%20couple.%E2%80%9D%20Another%20source%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CHarry%20appears%20focused%20on%20his%20patronage%20work%2C%20while%20Meghan%20is%20concentrating%20on%20her%20entrepreneurial%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20royal%20commentators%20and%20fans%20speculate%20that%20Meghan's%20decision%20to%20forgo%20her%20engagement%20ring%20might%20indicate%20deeper%20marital%20issues%2C%20others%20see%20it%20as%20a%20practical%20or%20style%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729080180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fm5a2ksoo_meghan-markle-afp-_625x300_09_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeghan-markle-seen-without-her-engagement-ring-at-california-event-6801727%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20engagement%20ring%2C%20which%20Harry%20designed%20with%20diamonds%20from%20his%20late%20mother%2C%20Princess%20Diana's%20collection%20and%20a%20stone%20from%20Botswana%2C%20has%20long%20held%20emotional%20significance%20for%20the%20couple.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeghan-markle-seen-without-her-engagement-ring-at-california-event-6801727%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EQT-backed%20Indium%20acquires%20majority%20stake%20in%20engineering%20firm%20Experion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729080180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F19%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1716133786-4174.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-backed-indium-acquires-majority-stake-in-engineering-firm-experion-124101600924_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20acquisition%20will%20expand%20Indium's%20geographic%20footprint%20and%20increase%20its%20headcount%20to%20approximately%205%2C000%20employees%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-backed-indium-acquires-majority-stake-in-engineering-firm-experion-124101600924_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-backed-indium-acquires-majority-stake-in-engineering-firm-experion-124101600924_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Feqt-backed-indium-acquires-majority-stake-in-engineering-firm-experion-124101600924_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Israel's%20Bulky%20Pagers%20Pulled%20A%20Devastating%20Attack%20On%20Hezbollah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20batteries%20inside%20the%20weaponised%20pagers%20that%20arrived%20in%20Lebanon%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20part%20of%20an%20Israeli%20plot%20to%20decimate%20Hezbollah%2C%20had%20powerfully%20deceptive%20features%20and%20an%20Achilles'%20heel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agents%20who%20built%20the%20pagers%20designed%20a%20battery%20that%20concealed%20a%20small%20but%20potent%20charge%20of%20plastic%20explosive%20and%20a%20novel%20detonator%20that%20was%20invisible%20to%20X-ray%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Lebanese%20source%20with%20first-hand%20knowledge%20of%20the%20pagers%2C%20and%20teardown%20photos%20of%20the%20battery%20pack%20seen%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20the%20weakness%20-%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20plausible%20backstory%20for%20the%20bulky%20new%20product%20-%20they%20created%20fake%20online%20stores%2C%20pages%20and%20posts%20that%20could%20deceive%20Hezbollah%20due%20diligence%2C%20a%20Reuters%20review%20of%20web%20archives%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stealthy%20design%20of%20the%20pager%20bomb%20and%20the%20battery's%20carefully%20constructed%20cover%20story%2C%20both%20described%20here%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20execution%20of%20a%20years-long%20operation%20which%20has%20struck%20unprecedented%20blows%20against%20Israel's%20Iran-backed%20Lebanese%20foe%20and%20pushed%20the%20Middle%20East%20closer%20to%20a%20regional%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20thin%2C%20square%20sheet%20with%20six%20grams%20of%20white%20pentaerythritol%20tetranitrate%20(PETN)%20plastic%20explosive%20was%20squeezed%20between%20two%20rectangular%20battery%20cells%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Lebanese%20source%20and%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20space%20between%20the%20battery%20cells%20could%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20photos%20but%20was%20occupied%20by%20a%20strip%20of%20highly%20flammable%20material%20that%20acted%20as%20the%20detonator%2C%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20three-layer%20sandwich%20was%20inserted%20in%20a%20black%20plastic%20sleeve%2C%20and%20encapsulated%20in%20a%20metal%20casing%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20a%20match%20box%2C%20the%20photos%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assembly%20was%20unusual%20because%20it%20did%20not%20rely%20on%20a%20standard%20miniaturised%20detonator%2C%20typically%20a%20metallic%20cylinder%2C%20the%20source%20and%20two%20bomb%20experts%20said.%20All%20three%20spoke%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20any%20metal%20components%2C%20the%20material%20used%20to%20trigger%20detonation%20had%20an%20edge%3A%20like%20the%20plastic%20explosives%2C%20it%20was%20not%20detected%20by%20X-ray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20receiving%20the%20pagers%20in%20February%2C%20Hezbollah%20looked%20for%20the%20presence%20of%20explosives%2C%20two%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said%2C%20putting%20them%20through%20airport%20security%20scanners%20to%20see%20if%20they%20triggered%20alarms.%20Nothing%20suspicious%20was%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20devices%20were%20likely%20set%20up%20to%20generate%20a%20spark%20within%20the%20battery%20pack%2C%20enough%20to%20light%20the%20detonating%20material%2C%20and%20trigger%20the%20sheet%20of%20PETN%20to%20explode%2C%20said%20the%20two%20bomb%20experts%2C%20to%20whom%20Reuters%20showed%20the%20pager-bomb%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20explosives%20and%20wrapping%20took%20about%20a%20third%20of%20the%20volume%2C%20the%20battery%20pack%20carried%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20power%20consistent%20with%20its%2035%20gram%20weight%2C%20two%20battery%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20unaccounted%20for%20mass%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Christensen%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20lithium%20batteries%20at%20Britain's%20Newcastle%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20Hezbollah%20noticed%20the%20battery%20was%20draining%20faster%20than%20expected%2C%20the%20Lebanese%20source%20said.%20However%2C%20the%20issue%20did%20not%20appear%20to%20raise%20major%20security%20concerns%20-%20the%20group%20was%20still%20handing%20its%20members%20the%20pagers%20hours%20before%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2017%2C%20thousands%20of%20pagers%20simultaneously%20exploded%20in%20the%20southern%20suburbs%20of%20Beirut%20and%20other%20Hezbollah%20strongholds%2C%20in%20most%20cases%20after%20the%20devices%20beeped%2C%20indicating%20an%20incoming%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20victims%20rushed%20to%20hospital%2C%20many%20had%20eye%20injuries%2C%20missing%20fingers%20or%20gaping%20holes%20in%20their%20abdomens%2C%20indicating%20their%20proximity%20to%20the%20devices%20at%20the%20time%20of%20detonation%2C%20Reuters%20witnesses%20saw.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20pager%20attack%2C%20and%20a%20second%20on%20the%20following%20day%20that%20activated%20weaponized%20walkie-talkies%2C%20killed%2039%20people%20and%20wounded%20more%20than%203%2C400.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20Western%20security%20sources%20said%20Israeli%20intelligence%20agency%20Mossad%20spearheaded%20the%20pager%20and%20walkie-talkie%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20could%20not%20establish%20where%20the%20devices%20were%20manufactured.%20The%20office%20of%20Israel's%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20which%20has%20authority%20over%20Mossad%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon's%20Information%20Ministry%20and%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Hezbollah%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20neither%20denied%20nor%20confirmed%20a%20role.%20The%20day%20after%20the%20attacks%20Israeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20praised%20Mossad's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20impressive%26quot%3B%20results%20in%20comments%20that%20were%20widely%20interpreted%20in%20Israel%20as%20a%20tacit%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20agency's%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20have%20said%20they%20were%20not%20informed%20of%20the%20operation%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20WEAK%20LINK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20outside%2C%20the%20pager's%20power%20source%20looked%20like%20a%20standard%20lithium-ion%20battery%20pack%20used%20in%20thousands%20of%20consumer%20electronics%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20the%20battery%2C%20labelled%20LI-BT783%2C%20had%20a%20problem%3A%20Like%20the%20pager%2C%20it%20did%20not%20exist%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Israel's%20agents%20created%20a%20backstory%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20has%20serious%20procurement%20procedures%20to%20check%20what%20they%20buy%2C%20a%20former%20Israeli%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20pager%20operation%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20if%20they%20look%2C%20they%20find%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20spy%20said%2C%20requesting%20not%20to%20be%20named.%20%26quot%3BNot%20finding%20anything%20is%20not%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20backstories%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Blegends%26quot%3B%2C%20for%20undercover%20agents%20has%20long%20been%20a%20core%20skill%20of%20spy%20agencies.%20What%20made%20the%20pager%20plot%20unusual%20is%20that%20those%20skills%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20applied%20to%20ubiquitous%20consumer%20electronics%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20pagers%2C%20the%20agents%20deceived%20Hezbollah%20by%20selling%20the%20custom-created%20model%2C%20AR-924%2C%20under%20an%20existing%2C%20renowned%20Taiwanese%20brand%2C%20Gold%20Apollo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20Apollo's%20chairman%2C%20Hsu%20Ching-kuang%2C%20told%20reporters%20a%20day%20after%20the%20pager%20attack%20that%20he%20was%20approached%20about%20three%20years%20ago%20by%20a%20former%20employee%2C%20Teresa%20Wu%2C%20and%20her%20%26quot%3Bbig%20boss%2C%20called%20Tom%26quot%3B%20to%20discuss%20a%20licence%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHsu%20said%20he%20had%20scant%20information%20about%20Wu's%20superior%2C%20but%20he%20granted%20them%20the%20right%20to%20design%20their%20own%20products%20and%20market%20them%20under%20the%20widely%20distributed%20Gold%20Apollo%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20could%20not%20establish%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20manager%2C%20nor%20whether%20the%20person%20or%20Wu%20knowingly%20worked%20with%20Israeli%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chairman%20said%20he%20was%20not%20impressed%20by%20the%20AR-924%20when%20he%20saw%20it%2C%20but%20still%20added%20photos%20and%20a%20description%20of%20the%20product%20to%20his%20company's%20website%2C%20helping%20give%20it%20both%20visibility%20and%20credibility.%20There%20was%20no%20way%20to%20directly%20buy%20the%20AR-924%20from%20his%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHsu%20said%20he%20knew%20nothing%20about%20the%20pagers'%20lethal%20capabilities%20or%20the%20broader%20operation%20to%20attack%20Hezbollah.%20He%20described%20his%20company%20as%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20Apollo%20declined%20to%20provide%20further%20comment.%20Calls%20and%20messages%20sent%20to%20Wu%20went%20unanswered.%20She%20has%20not%20given%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20media%20since%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20KNOW%20THIS%20PRODUCT%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202023%2C%20webpages%20and%20images%20featuring%20the%20AR-924%20and%20its%20battery%20were%20added%20to%20apollosystemshk.com%2C%20a%20website%20that%20said%20it%20had%20a%20licence%20to%20distribute%20Gold%20Apollo%20products%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rugged%20pager%20and%20its%20bulky%20power%20source%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Reuters%20review%20of%20internet%20records%20and%20metadata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20gave%20an%20address%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20for%20a%20company%20called%20Apollo%20Systems%20HK.%20No%20company%20by%20that%20name%20exists%20at%20the%20address%20or%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20Corporate%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20website%20was%20listed%20by%20Wu%2C%20the%20Taiwanese%20businesswoman%2C%20on%20her%20Facebook%20page%20as%20well%20as%20in%20public%20incorporation%20records%20when%20she%20registered%20a%20company%20called%20Apollo%20Systems%20in%20Taipei%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20apollosystemshk.com%20site%20devoted%20to%20the%20LI-BT783%20put%20emphasis%20on%20the%20battery's%20outstanding%20performance.%20Unlike%20the%20disposable%20batteries%20that%20powered%20older%20generation%20pagers%2C%20it%20boasted%2085%20days%20of%20autonomy%20and%20could%20be%20recharged%20via%20a%20USB%20cable%2C%20according%20to%20the%20website%20and%20a%2090-second%20promotional%20video%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202023%2C%20two%20battery%20stores%20came%20online%20with%20the%20LI-BT783%20listed%20in%20their%20catalogues%2C%20Reuters%20found.%20And%20in%20two%20online%20forums%20devoted%20to%20batteries%2C%20participants%20discussed%20the%20power%20source%2C%20despite%20its%20lack%20of%20commercial%20availability%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20this%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20with%20the%20handle%20Mikevog%20wrote%20in%20April%202023.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20got%20a%20great%20datasheet%20and%20a%20great%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20could%20not%20establish%20the%20identity%20of%20Mikevog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20website%2C%20the%20online%20stores%2C%20and%20the%20forum%20discussions%20bear%20the%20hallmark%20of%20a%20deception%20effort%2C%20the%20former%20Israeli%20intelligence%20officer%20and%20two%20Western%20security%20officers%20told%20Reuters.%20The%20websites%20have%20been%20scrubbed%20from%20the%20web%20since%20the%20pager%20bombs%20devastated%20Lebanon%2C%20but%20archived%20and%20cached%20copies%20are%20still%20viewable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuing%20the%20day%20they%20bought%20the%20pagers%2C%20Hezbollah%20leaders%20said%20they%20had%20launched%20internal%20investigations%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20security%20breach%20could%20happen%20and%20identify%20possible%20moles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20had%20shifted%20to%20pagers%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%20after%20realising%20that%20cellphone%20communications%20were%20compromised%20by%20Israeli%20eavesdropping%2C%20Reuters%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah's%20investigations%20have%20helped%20uncover%20how%20Israeli%20agents%20used%20an%20aggressive%20sales%20tactic%20to%20make%20sure%20Hezbollah's%20procurement%20manager%20chose%20the%20AR-924%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20salesperson%20who%20conveyed%20the%20offer%20made%20a%20very%20inexpensive%20proposition%20for%20the%20pagers%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20kept%20bringing%20the%20price%20down%20until%20he%20was%20pulled%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanese%20authorities%20have%20condemned%20the%20attacks%20as%20a%20serious%20violation%20of%20Lebanon's%20sovereignty.%20On%20September%2019%2C%20in%20his%20last%20public%20speech%20before%20he%20was%20killed%20by%20Israel%2C%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Sayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20said%20the%20device%20blasts%20could%20amount%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeclaration%20of%20war%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20to%20punish%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20and%20Israel%20have%20been%20exchanging%20fire%20since%20October%208%2C%202023%2C%20when%20the%20operator%20group%20began%20launching%20rockets%20at%20Israeli%20military%20positions%20in%20solidarity%20with%20its%20Palestinian%20ally%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20device%20attacks%2C%20Israel%20has%20launched%20a%20full-on%20war%20on%20Hezbollah%2C%20including%20a%20ground%20invasion%20of%20southern%20Lebanon%20and%20airstrikes%20that%20have%20killed%20most%20of%20its%20top%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah's%20internal%20investigation%20into%20the%20pager%20attack%2C%20still%20underway%2C%20suffered%20a%20setback%20on%20September%2028%3A%20Eleven%20days%20after%20the%20devices%20exploded%2C%20the%20senior%20Hezbollah%20official%20tasked%20with%20leading%20the%20procurement%20probe%2C%20Nabil%20Kaouk%2C%20was%20himself%20killed%20by%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729080060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgn7ubojo_hezbollah-pager-attacks_625x300_19_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israels-bulky-pagers-pulled-a-devastating-attack-on-hezbollah-6802991%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20batteries%20inside%20the%20weaponised%20pagers%20that%20arrived%20in%20Lebanon%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20part%20of%20an%20Israeli%20plot%20to%20decimate%20Hezbollah%2C%20had%20powerfully%20deceptive%20features%20and%20an%20Achilles'%20heel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israels-bulky-pagers-pulled-a-devastating-attack-on-hezbollah-6802991%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%20Game%20Company%20FunPlus%20Launches%20Lisbon-Ba