tional%20parties%20and%20four%20prominent%20formations%3A%20the%20two%20factions%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%20Additionally%2C%20other%20parties%20represent%20various%20sections%2C%20including%20the%20Dalits%20and%20Ambedkarites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20little%20over%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20two%20strongest%20regional%20outfits%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20founded%20by%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%2C%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20led%20by%20prominent%20Maratha%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20saw%20deep%20splits.%20The%20respective%20breakaway%20factions%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20respectively%2C%20were%20later%20recognised%20as%20the%20official%20parties%20and%20gained%20the%20right%20to%20use%20their%20party%20symbols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20five%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20delivered%20a%20verdict%20that%20enhanced%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20moral%20authority%20as%20the%20true%20inheritors%20of%20their%20respective%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20Results%20Indicate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20convert%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20assembly%20constituencies%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20leading%20with%2083%20seats%2C%20followed%20by%20Congress%20with%2063.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20has%2056%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20other%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%2038.%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20secured%2032%20seats%2C%20with%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20trailing%20with%20just%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20dynamics%20for%20state%20elections%20differ%20significantly%20from%20those%20at%20play%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20issues%20are%20distinct%2C%20as%20is%20the%20voter%20approach.%20For%20instance%2C%20this%20summer%2C%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20influencing%20voters%20was%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Modi%20government%20was%20seeking%20a%20400-plus%20majority%20to%20alter%20the%20Constitution.%20This%20concern%20alone%20consolidated%20votes%20against%20the%20incumbent%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20electoral%20race%20takes%20shape%2C%20two%20major%20coalitions%20dominate%20the%20landscape%3A%20Mahayuti%2C%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20along%20with%20the%20two%20official%20factions%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%2C%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%2C%20which%20comprises%20Congress%20and%20the%20other%20two%20factions%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP.%20The%20presence%20of%20senior%20Pawar%20marks%20a%20significant%20difference%20in%20this%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Pawar%20Magic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wily%20octogenarian%20politician%20demonstrated%20his%20skill%20in%20forging%20an%20unlikely%20coalition%2C%20bringing%20together%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Congress%20to%20share%20power.%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20traditionally%20a%20hard-core%20Hindutva%20party%20and%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20BJP%20allies%2C%20made%20this%20shift%20for%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20Sharad%20Pawar%20once%20again%20pull%20a%20rabbit%20out%20of%20the%20hat%3F%20The%20upcoming%20polls%20should%20clarify%20the%20future%20and%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20especially%20since%20his%20understudy%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20has%20chosen%20to%20be%20a%20junior%20partner%20in%20the%20Shinde%20government.%20Senior%20Pawar's%20daughter%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20is%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20a%20seamless%20leadership%20transition.%20The%20outcome%20on%20November%2023%20will%20determine%20the%20course%20ahead.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBoth%20the%20Mahayuti%20and%20the%20MVA%20face%20the%20tough%20decision%20of%20whether%20to%20present%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20or%20go%20to%20the%20people%20with%20an%20element%20of%20suspense%20about%20who%20that%20candidate%20might%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20holds%20a%20distinct%20advantage.%20Retaining%20the%20right%20to%20govern%20Haryana%20gives%20the%20BJP%20a%20significant%20psychological%20edge%20over%20its%20challengers.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20chastised%20by%20its%20stunning%20defeat%20in%20Haryana%2C%20should%20learn%20valuable%20lessons%20and%20focus%20on%20capitalising%20on%20the%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%20facing%20the%20Shinde%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Complex%20Landscape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20a%20fragmented%20political%20landscape%2C%20voters%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20select%20the%20best%20representatives%20who%20can%20embody%20the%20pride%20of%20being%20Maharashtrian%20while%20continuing%20to%20drive%20the%20industrious%20and%20prosperous%20state%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplicating%20matters%20is%20the%20deep%20distress%20in%20the%20agrarian%20sector%2C%20marked%20by%20farmer%20suicides%20and%20drought-prone%20areas%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20confound%20policy%20planners.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20is%20the%20ongoing%20demand%20for%20reservation%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%20with%20an%20active%20campaign%20in%20place.%20How%20this%20demand%20will%20align%20with%20the%20concerns%20of%20communities%20benefiting%20from%20affirmative%20action%20remains%20an%20unclear%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20juxtaposed%20with%20welfare%20measures%20introduced%20by%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Ladki%20Bahin%20Yojna%2C%20which%20provides%20cash%20to%20families%20with%20girl%20children.%20A%20similar%20scheme%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20swayed%20voters%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp