him%20so%20he%20would%20look%20like%20a%20little%20German%20hiker.%20I'd%20sing%20to%20him%20as%20we%20wandered%20together.%20Though%20he%20couldn't%20walk%2C%20he%20was%20so%20excited%20to%20see%20so%20much.%20I%20kept%20a%20few%20pieces%20of%20clothing%20from%20that%20trip.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20like%20opening%20a%20photobook%20that%20you%20haven't%20looked%20at%20in%20years%2C%20except%20it%20was%20in%203D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESitting%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20clothes%20all%20around%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F90s-kid-things-the-internet-wont-let-die-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estrong%20sense%20of%20nostalgia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20an%20overwhelming%20love%20for%20my%20kids.%20I%20loved%20mothering%20them%20so%20much.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20special%20time%20in%20my%20life%20and%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20my%20identity.%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20to%20raise%20them%2C%20pouring%20everything%20into%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d22c0f0a-09f5-4eec-a11a-4076e40b2fc9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20early%20days%20of%20motherhood%20are%20unique%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20those%20early%20days%2C%20when%20they%20were%20completely%20bound%20to%20me%2C%20I%20bonded%20with%20them%20in%20such%20an%20intense%20way%2C%20present%20for%20them%20at%20every%20moment.%20Normally%2C%20I'm%20not%20sentimental%2C%20but%20those%20early%20days%20of%20motherhood%20are%20unique.%20It%20was%20different%20from%20anything%20else%20I've%20done%20in%20my%20life.%20These%20clothes%20weren't%20just%20a%20piece%20of%20them%2C%20but%20a%20piece%20of%20myself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20was%20going%20through%20the%20clothes%2C%20I%20texted%20my%20kids%20to%20see%20if%20they%20wanted%20me%20to%20set%20anything%20aside%20for%20them.%20They%20both%20told%20me%20to%20throw%20it%20all%20out.%20They%20obviously%20couldn't%20remember%20wearing%20them%20and%20had%20no%20interest%20in%20saving%20them%20in%20case%20they%20had%20their%20own%20kids%20one%20day.%20I%20certainly%20don't%20want%20them%20to%20carry%20my%20burden%20of%20sentimentality%20%E2%80%94%20that%20would%20be%20so%20unfair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20the%20only%20person%20in%20the%20world%20to%20whom%20these%20tiny%20pieces%20of%20clothing%20mattered%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20one%20who%20held%20the%20memories%20attached%20to%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221cf67263-e072-48ae-8811-236734a290fa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20went%20through%20every%20outfit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20didn't%20just%20want%20to%20go%20through%20and%20get%20rid%20of%20them%20thoughtlessly%20%E2%80%94%20they%20aren't%20garbage.%20Instead%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20through%20each%20outfit%20respectfully%20and%20slowly%2C%20remembering%20the%20moments%20my%20children%20wore%20each.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWashing%20them%20all%20and%20then%20folding%20them%2C%20I%20decided%20on%20what%20I%20would%20keep%20and%20what%20I%20would%20give%20away%20to%20other%20young%20mothers.%20I%20only%20kept%20a%20few%20pieces%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20else%20has%20been%20put%20to%20one%20side%20to%20give%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'll%20never%20have%20another%20human%20being%20attached%20to%20me%2C%20like%20when%20my%20kids%20were%20babies%2C%20and%20their%20clothes%20represented%20that%20for%20me.%20I'm%20sad%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20them%2C%20but%20hopeful%20they%20will%20go%20on%20to%20give%20another%20the%20same%20joy%20as%20they%20have%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdownsizing-going-through-baby-clothes-donating-motherhood-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729075321000