ourism_625x300_16_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20as%20a%20travel%20destination%20suffers%20from%20an%20image%20issue.%20And%20its%20popular%20tourism%20mottos%2C%20'Atithi%20devo%20bhava'%20or%20'Incredible%20India'%2C%20aren't%20doing%20much%20to%20change%20the%20perception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20findings%20of%20a%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Booking.com%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%25%20of%20foreign%20travellers%20to%20India%20listed%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20sick%26quot%3B%20as%20their%20biggest%20concern%2C%20while%2027%25%20international%20travellers%20to%20India%20mentioned%20%26quot%3Bsafety%20and%20security%26quot%3B%20as%20their%20biggest%20worry.%20Cultural%20differences%20(13%25)%20and%20language%20barriers%20(12%25)%20were%20also%20cited%20as%20other%20concerns.%20Health%20and%20safety%20issues%20were%20also%20the%20biggest%20factors%20cited%20by%20foreign%20tourists%20who%20visited%20India%20but%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%2C%20specific%20to%20India's%20inbound%20travel%20trends%2C%20was%20conducted%20in%20August%20and%20involved%202%2C000%20adults%20from%2019%20countries%2C%20also%20mentions%20that%20other%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries%20are%20attracting%20more%20travellers%20due%20to%20their%20easy%20visa%20regimes%20and%20value-for-money%20propositions%20for%20tourists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20India%20Has%20Lagged%20Behind%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20tourist%20arrivals%20in%20India%20have%20remained%20well%20below%20pre-pandemic%20levels%2C%20despite%20a%20recovery%20in%202023.%20It%20reached%204.78%20million%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024%2C%20showing%20a%20recovery%20from%204.38%20million%20in%202023%2C%20but%20still%20short%20of%20pre-Covid%20figures%20of%205.29%20million%20in%202019.%20Interestingly%2C%20more%20Indians%20are%20now%20travelling%20abroad.%20But%20proportionately%2C%20fewer%20foreign%20tourists%20are%20coming%20into%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20may%20be%20a%20welcoming%20country%2C%20but%20our%20visa%20process%20is%20cumbersome.%20We%20may%20have%20constructed%20roads%20and%20metros%20but%20we%20still%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20match%20infrastructure-friendly%20countries%2C%20including%20some%20Southeast%20Asian%20nations%2C%20where%20travel%20is%20comparatively%20easy%2C%20organised%20and%20reasonable.%20Lack%20of%20quality%20budget%20hotels%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20organised%20transportation%20are%20a%20few%20reasons%20that%20dissuade%20foreign%20tourists%20from%20coming%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustry%20bodies%20feel%20that%20this%20is%20largely%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20aggressive%20marketing%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20tourism%20offices%20in%20key%20markets.%20%26quot%3BOur%20marketing%20and%20promotions%20are%20not%20up%20to%20the%20level%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries.%20The%20roadshows%20by%20Malaysia%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20the%20visa%20facilitation%20by%20them%2C%20including%20by%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20make%20them%20destinations%20of%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rajiv%20Mehra%2C%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20Tour%20Operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20tourists%2C%20particularly%20women%2C%20feel%20India%20is%20an%20unsafe%20place%20to%20travel%20to.%20Frequent%20news%20reports%20about%20rape%20and%20harassment%20also%20worry%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20that%2C%20factors%20like%20insensitive%20immigration%20officials%2C%20the%20scourge%20of%20touts%2C%20chaotic%20airport%20arrivals%2C%20unhygienic%20locations%20and%20food%2C%20also%20leave%20a%20very%20negative%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20small%20country%20like%20Vietnam%2C%20an%20emerging%20tourist%20destination%2C%20has%20better%20roads%2C%20and%20better%20tourist%20infrastructure%20like%20buses%2C%20trains%2C%20coaches%20and%20taxis%2C%20and%20is%20very%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ECapitalising%20On%20Buddhist%20Circuits%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20tourism%20downturn%2C%20India%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20infrastructural%20improvements%20and%20targeted%20marketing%20campaigns.%20Direct%20international%20air%20connectivity%20and%20simplification%20of%20visa%20processes%20can%20help%20India%20promote%20itself%20as%20a%20global%20tourist%20destination.%20%26quot%3BAirfares%20going%20northwards%20is%20another%20deterrent.%20Unprecedented%20demand%20for%20big%20fat%20weddings%20among%20Indians%20has%20pushed%20hotel%20rates%20by%2025%25%20in%20places%20like%20Udaipur%20and%20Goa%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mehra.%20%26quot%3BThe%20GST%20amount%20is%20very%20high%20in%20India%20compared%20to%20other%20countries.%20For%20example%2C%20against%20India's%2023%25%20GST%2C%20France%20charges%2010%25%2C%20UK%2015%25%2C%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20China%20between%207%25%20to%208%25%2C%20etc.%20This%20has%20made%20India's%20in-bound%20tourism%20sector%20extremely%20uncompetitive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20huge%20potential%20of%20its%20Buddhist%20heritage%20and%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20popularise%20its%20Buddhist%20circuits.%20Destinations%20like%20Bodh%20Gaya%2C%20Rajgir%2C%20Nalanda%2C%20Kushinagar%2C%20Dharamshala%2C%20Ladakh%2C%20etc%2C%20fail%20to%20attract%20significant%20numbers%20of%20tourists%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20cleanliness%2C%20amenities%20and%20safety.%20This%20is%20ironic%20as%20there%20are%20a%20large%20numbers%20of%20Buddhists%20in%20China%2C%20Japan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Central%20and%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries%2C%20a%20tourist%20market%20India%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20tap.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20not%20all%20is%20bleak.%20There%20were%20some%20optimistic%20messages%20in%20the%20survey%20as%20well.%20As%20many%20as%2040%25%20responders%20said%20they%20had%20never%20been%20to%20India%20but%20planned%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20attract%20foreign%20tourists%2C%20the%20Indian%20tourism%20industry%20must%20up%20its%20hospitality%20game.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20better%20coordination%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%20to%20enhance%20the%20visitors'%20experience.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20been%20promoting%20domestic%20tourism%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20But%20the%20ministry%20must%20focus%20on%20prioritising%20the%20foreign%20tourist%20sector%20too%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20crucial%20means%20for%20both%20economic%20and%20socio-cultural%20exchange.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729067580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fu15nkf08_tourism_625x300_16_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-foreign-tourists-hesitate-to-visit-india-6801585%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20attract%20foreign%20tourists%2C%20the%20Indian%20tourism%20industry%20must%20up%20its%20hospitality%20game.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20better%20coordination%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%20to%20enhance%20the%20visitors'%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-foreign-tourists-hesitate-to-visit-india-6801585%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kenyan%20deputy%20president's%20impeachment%20trial%20begins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729067239000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F4446%2Flive%2F984ecde0-8b84-11ef-a3f4-b76c852e8a2b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgryvj4q5y7o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22T