%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShould%20Recognise%20Territorial%20Integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20S%20Jaishankar%20In%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20cooperation%20based%20on%20mutual%20respect%2C%20in%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO)%20Summit%20in%20Pakistan%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%20to%20Pakistan%20since%20Sushma%20Swaraj's%202015%20tour%2C%20Jaishankar%20called%20terrorism%2C%20extremism%20and%20separatism%20%26quot%3Bthree%20evils%26quot%3B.%20He%C2%A0added%20that%20cooperation%20between%20countries%20is%20built%20on%20genuine%20partnerships%2C%20not%20unilateral%20agendas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20mentioned%20the%20Israel-Hamas-Hezbollah%20and%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflicts%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20to%20state%20that%20the%20summit%20comes%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20time%20in%20world%20affairs%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BDisruptions%20of%20various%C2%A0kinds%20%E2%80%93%20ranging%20from%20extreme%20climate%20events%20to%20supply%20chain%20uncertainties%20and%20financial%20volatility%20%E2%80%93%20impact%20growth%20and%20development.%20Debt%20is%20a%20serious%20concern%2C%20even%20as%20the%20world%20falls%20behind%20in%20achieving%20Sustainable%20Development%20targets.%20Technology%20holds%20great%20promise%2C%20as%20well%20as%20raising%20a%20new%20host%20of%20concerns.%20How%20should%20the%20members%20of%20the%20SCO%20respond%20to%20these%20challenges%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EAM%20also%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%C2%A0multi-faceted%20regional%20cooperation%2C%20to%20drive%20growth%20and%20conflict%20prevention.%20%26quot%3BActivities%20across%20borders%20characterised%20by%20terrorism%20and%20extremism%20are%20unlikely%20to%20encourage%20trade%2C%20energy%20flows%2C%20connectivity%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20arrived%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20his%20two-day%20Pakistan%20visit%20at%20Rawalpindi's%20Nur%20Khan%20Airbase%2C%20where%20he%20was%20welcomed%20by%20Ilyas%20Mehmood%20Nizami%2C%20Director%20General%20(South%20Asia)%20of%20Pakistan's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs.%20Children%20dressed%20in%20traditional%20attire%20presented%20him%20with%20flower%20bouquets.%C2%A0Later%2C%20he%C2%A0had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdecade-of-no-dialogue-then-a-20-second-greeting-india-pakistan-de-hyphenated-6797302%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrief%20interaction%20with%C2%A0Pakistan's%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20at%20an%20official%20dinner%20held%20for%20all%20the%20summit%20attendees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20meeting%20of%20SCO%20CHG%2C%20the%20second%20highest%20forum%20within%20the%20SCO%2C%C2%A0is%20being%20chaired%20by%20Pakistan's%20Prime%20Minister%20Sharif%20as%20the%20current%20chair%20of%20the%20Council.%C2%A0The%20meeting's%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20trade%20and%20economic%20agenda%20of%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%C2%A0Sharif%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20called%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20China's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%20to%20enhance%20regional%20cooperation.%20%26quot%3BFlagship%20projects%20like%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20of%20President%20Xi%20Jinping...should%20be%20expanded%20focusing%20on%20developing%20road%2C%20rail%20and%20digital%20infrastructure%20that%20enhances%20integration%20and%20cooperation%20across%20our%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharif%20said%20in%20his%20speech%20as%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRI%20is%20a%20%241%20trillion%20plan%20for%20global%20infrastructure%20and%20energy%20networks%20that%20China%20launched%20a%20decade%20ago%20to%20connect%20Asia%20with%20Africa%20and%20Europe%20through%20land%20and%20maritime%20routes.%20Sharif%20said%20CPEC%20would%20also%20help%20enhance%20cooperation%2C%20adding%20that%2040%20percent%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20lived%20in%20SCO's%2010%20full%20member%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharif%20also%C2%A0called%20on%20the%20leaders%20to%20use%20the%20SCO%20meeting%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexchange%20ideas%2C%20share%20best%20practices%20and%20forge%20concrete%20action%20plans%20that%20will%20benefit%20our%20economies%20and%20societies%E2%80%9D.%20He%20expressed%20his%20hope%20for%20%E2%80%9Cwonderful%20outcomes%20that%20will%20emerge%20from%20our%20in-depth%20deliberations%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%E2%80%9COur%20collaboration%2C%20joint%20teamwork%20expands%20academic%20and%20tourism%20linkages%2C%20poverty%20alleviation%2C%20empowerment%20of%20women%20and%20youth%20across%20the%20SCO%20region%20are%20reflection%20and%20commitment%20of%20our%20determination%20to%20promote%20prosperity%20through%20unity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCO%20comprises%20China%2C%20India%2C%20Russia%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Iran%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Kyrgyzstan%2C%20Tajikistan%2C%20Uzbekistan%20and%20Belarus%20%E2%80%94%20with%2016%20more%20countries%20affiliated%20as%20observers%20or%20%E2%80%9Cdialogue%20partners%E2%80%9D.%20The%20group%20claims%20to%20represent%2040%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20and%20about%2030%20percent%20of%20its%20GDP.%C2%A0Pakistan%20became%20a%20full%20member%20of%20the%20SCO%20at%20its%202017%20summit%20in%20Kazakhstan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E-%20With%20inputs%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729065840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F0m8abo38_s-jaishankar-shehbaz-sharif-ani_625x300_15_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcooperation-must-be-on-mutual-respect-says-s-jaishankar-in-pakistan-6800735%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22External%20Afairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20emphasised%20the%20nee