leena%E2%80%99s%20mother-in-law%20urged%20the%20doctors%20to%20remove%20the%20ovary%20during%20the%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20most%20cases%2C%20especially%20with%20women%20of%20childbearing%20age%2C%20doctors%20usually%20try%20to%20save%20the%20ovary%2C%20but%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20further%20complications%20and%20more%20surgeries.%20I%20come%20from%20a%20very%20progressive%20family%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20most%20people%20will%20take%20that%20stand.%20I%20know%20of%20friends%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t%20even%20asked%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20child.%20Doctors%20decided%20for%20them%20and%20saved%20the%20ovary.%20They%20had%20to%20undergo%20another%20surgery%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devleena%20shares.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369525%2Frama-world-mental-health-anxiety-disorder-slow-down-hustle-culture-journalist-breaking-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20agency%20and%20their%20wishes%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren%E2%80%99t%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20she%20rues.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20doctors%20advise%20you%20to%20have%20children%20as%20it%20might%20sort%20out%20some%20issues%20according%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESneha%20also%20chimes%20in.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%2025%20and%20not%20married.%20The%20doctor%20suggested%20that%20I%20should%20think%20of%20having%20a%20child%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20women%20have%20finally%20found%20solutions%20to%20their%20pain%20after%20years%20of%20struggles.%20Speaking%20to%20many%20other%20women%20in%20the%20same%20boat%2C%20they%20say%20that%20the%20consensus%20remains%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20their%20pain%20is%20not%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20level%20of%20pain%20is%20not%20normal.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20have%20the%20information%20to%20understand%20what%20your%20body%20is%20going%20through.%20Just%20knowing%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20in%20my%20head%20was%20hugely%20empowering%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devleena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20a%20pain%20like%20this%20normalised%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Sneha.%20%E2%80%9CPain%20is%20not%20a%20normal%20physiological%20process.%20Pain%20is%20not%20part%20of%20being%20a%20woman.%20This%20whole%20%E2%80%98women%20need%20to%20endure%20pain%E2%80%99%20mentality%20needs%20to%20stop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20build%20a%20%23BetterIndiaForWomen%2C%20both%20women%20assert%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20medical%20professionals%20started%20listening%20to%20women.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20time%20women%20start%20taking%20their%20health%20seriously.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20listen%20and%20indulge%20women%20who%20come%20seeking%20help%20from%20you.%20Hear%20us%20out.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20in%20our%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20reiterates%20Sneha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20your%20pain%20is%20bad%20and%20not%20something%20you%E2%80%99ve%20experienced%20before%2C%20go%20to%20a%20doctor.%20Find%20one%20who%20listens%20to%20you%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up.%20Start%20taking%20care%20of%20yourself%20and%20give%20priority%20to%20your%20own%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728564604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-06-at-11.44.48-min-1728551721.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Devleena%20Chatterjee%20and%20Sneha%20Khedkar%20share%20their%20stories%20of%20living%20with%20debilitating%20pain%20every%20month.%20Doctors%20sent%20them%20home%20with%20painkillers%20saying%20that%20they%20had%20a%20lower%20tolerance%20for%20pa