nselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egeneralised%20anxiety%20disorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mental%20health%20condition%20characterised%20by%20excessive%20fear%20and%20worry%20about%20everyday%20activities%20and%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EShocked%20by%20the%20diagnosis%2C%20Rama%2C%2044%2C%20found%20solace%20in%20her%20psychiatrist%E2%80%99s%20words%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20pull%20you%20out%20of%20this.%20If%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20help%20me%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20help%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20statement%20made%20a%20world%20of%20difference%20as%20Rama%20finally%20understood%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20persistent%20worries%2C%20sleepless%20nights%2C%20and%20anxiety%20about%20the%20future%20over%20the%20past%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20her%20story%20and%20how%20it%20took%20physical%20pain%20to%20diagnose%20her%20mental%20struggles%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20gripped%20by%20a%20fear%20of%20the%20future%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Rama%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20in%202018%20for%20a%20job.%20Adjusting%20to%20a%20new%20city%2C%20culture%2C%20people%2C%20and%20workplace%20was%20challenging%20for%20her%2C%20especially%20while%20living%20alone.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20easy%20coming%20home%20to%20an%20empty%20apartment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits%20candidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20hindsight%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20living%20alone%20triggered%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F173434%2Fkerala-free-mental-health-care-doctor-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20episodes%20of%20anxiety.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Deeply%20ambitious%2C%20she%20had%20charted%20out%20a%20path%20for%20herself%2C%20and%20when%20things%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20as%20planned%2C%20they%20affected%20her%20deeply.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20realise%20I%20was%20anxious%20or%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%20I%20would%20have%20palpitations%20but%20somehow%20powered%20through%20as%20I%20had%20work%20to%20finish%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rama%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20a%20fast-paced%20setup%20where%20breaking%20news%20took%20priority%20and%20daily%20newspaper%20editions%20had%20to%20be%20sent%20out%2C%20she%20often%20neglected%20her%20own%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20I%20never%20understood%20its%20importance.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20up%20for%20what%20I%20needed.%20Taking%20a%20break%20or%20slowing%20down%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20you%E2%80%99re%20doing%20less%2C%20as%20I%20now%20realise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Ftips-to-cope-with-anxiety-1728485507.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Ftips-to-cope-with-anxiety-1728485507.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Ftips-to-cope-with-anxiety-1728485507-300x162.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Ftips-to-cope-with-anxiety-1728485507-500x269.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Ftips-to-cope-with-anxiety-1728485507-768x413.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Ftips-to-cope-with-anxiety-1728485507-150x81.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369535%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22646%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20features%20section%20of%20her%20organisation%20shut%20down%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Rama%20found%20herself%20without%20a%20job%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20underwent%20surgery%20for%20a%20deviated%20septum%20(a%20condition%20where%20the%20cartilage%20and%20bone%20that%20separate%20the%20nasal%20cavity%20are%20off-centre).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-surgery%20complications%20triggered%20her%20anxiety%2C%20and%20she%20was%20particularly%20afraid%20of%20losing%20her%20hearing.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sleep%20for%2010%20whole%20days%20and%20had%20constant%20palpitations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20like%20the%20world%20was%20closing%20in%20on%20me%2C%20and%20my%20vision%20was%20beginning%20to%20blur%20when%20I%20was%20on%20the%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rama%20explains.%20This%20anxiety%20led%20her%20to%20consult%20multiple%20ENT%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20asking%20the%20doctor%20for%20medication%20to%20make%20me%20feel%20better.%20Finally%2C%20one%20fine%20day%2C%20she%20told%20me%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20my%20ear.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20really%20think%20you%20have%20anxiety%20and%20should%20visit%20a%20psychiatrist%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Bengaluru%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20psychiatrist%20was%20an%20eye-opener.%20As%20she%20discussed%20her%20symptoms%2C%20the%20psychiatrist%20diagnosed%20her%20with%20generalised%20anxiety%20disorder.%20What%20troubled%20her%20the%20most%20was%20that%20as%20a%20journalist%20who%20had%20covered%20and%20commissioned%20several%20health%20stories%2C%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20recognised%20her%20own%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20I%20notice%20the%20signs%3F%20I%20realised%20we%20get%20so%20caught%20up%20in%20work.%20Newsrooms%20are%20chaotic%2C%20deadlines%20are%20relentless%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20think%20about%20our%20health.%20Even%20when%20we%20rest%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20still%20working.%20I%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20rest.%20Rest%2C%20to%20me%2C%20meant%20anxiety%20because%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20doing%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Slow%20down%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20was%20bogged%20down%20by%20a%20constant%20fear%20of%20the%20future%2C%20which%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20her%20to%20sleep.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feared%20failure%20and%20not%20being%20able%20to%20achieve%20my%20goals.%20I%20had%20cold%20feet%20and%20palpitations.%20Fear%20had%20invaded%20my%20body.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20psychiatrist%20gave%20her%20some%20pills%20to%20begin%20her%20treatment.%20Rama%20also%20called%20her%20mother%20to%20Bengaluru%20for%20support%20while%20her%20husband%20was%20at%20work.%20She%20stayed%20with%20her%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20providing%20unwavering%20support%20every%20time%20Rama%20broke%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20her%20mother%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F315631%2Fbengaluru-punita-mittal-mahak-maheshwari-soulup-mental-health-online-support-platform%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstand%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20listened.%20They%20would%20go%20on%20long%20walks%2C%20sometimes%20lasting%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20which%20helped%20Rama%20get%20fresh%20air%2C%20sunlight%2C%20and%20a%20much-needed%20distraction%20from%20her%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20notes%20that%20while%20loved%20ones%20may%20not%20fully%20understand%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20they%20can%20still%20help.%20Over%20time%2C%20her%20husband%20became%20more%20receptive%20to%20her%20needs%20and%20worked%20alongside%20her%20to%20help%20her%20feel%2