0anymore.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20anything%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20me%20to%20rest%20or%20impacts%20my%20mental%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20if%20she%20had%20a%20time%20machine%2C%20she%20would%20probably%20have%20sought%20help%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20my%20life%20would%20have%20been%20very%20different%20if%20I%20had%20viewed%20rest%20as%20a%20necessity%2C%20not%20a%20luxury.%20Had%20I%20known%20that%20taking%20rest%20breaks%20in%20my%20career%20would%20have%20helped%20me%20stay%20healthy%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20I%20would%20have%20done%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20know%20someone%20with%20anxiety%2C%20just%20hear%20them%20out%2C%20she%20advises.%20Check-in%20on%20them%20regularly%20and%20lend%20an%20ear!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20every%20person%20fighting%20their%20own%20mental%20battles%2C%20she%20has%20an%20important%20message%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMental%20health%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%20If%20your%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331532%2Ftherapy-in-chennai-mental-health-cafe-wellness-centre-pooja-srinivasa-love-hope-company%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn%E2%80%99t%20in%20a%20good%20place%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20you%20do%2C%20your%20physical%20health%20won%E2%80%99t%20hold%20up.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20care%20of%20this%2C%20you%20cannot%20achieve%20anything%20else.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20one-month%20or%20six-month%20journey%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20lifelong%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728486360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https