ty%20members%20in%20decision-making%20and%20foster%20a%20collective%20effort%20to%20tackle%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20assistance%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Prasanna%20through%20the%20Dhwani%20National%20Domestic%20Violence%20Hotline%20at%201800-102-7282%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eand%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcvconline.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Prasanna%20Gettu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS%20%E2%80%93%205)%2C%202019%E2%80%9321%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Published%20by%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Population%20Sciences%20(IIPS)%20and%20ICF.%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728396571000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20third%20ever-married%20women%20in%20India%20experiences%20physical%2C%20sexual%2C%20or%20emotional%20violence%20by%20their%20husbands%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20Despite%20such%20atrocious%20cruelty%2C%20many%20cases%20go%20unreported.%20Prasanna%20Gettu%20suggests%20five%20ways%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20respect%2C%20equality%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20working%20towards%20creating%20a%20society%20where%20violence%20is%20not%20tolerated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369214%2Fprasanna-